---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import RiskBanner from '@/components/RiskBanner.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About PipFury" description="PipFury is built against trading hype: evidence, risk, invalidation, and honest review.">
<section class="section"><div class="container grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_360px]"><article class="terminal-card p-8 md:p-10"><span class="pill">About</span><h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-5xl font-bold">Built against trading hype.</h1><p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-muted">PipFury is a forex education brand focused on VSA, Smart Money Concepts, price action, psychology, and transparent review.</p><div class="my-8"><RiskBanner /></div><div class="prose"><h2>What PipFury teaches</h2><p>It teaches traders to separate evidence from assumption: context, volume, spread, liquidity, structure, invalidation, execution, and review.</p><h2>What PipFury does not do</h2><p>PipFury does not sell signals, promise profits, hide losses, publish fake testimonials, or present educational analysis as financial advice.</p><h2>Philosophy</h2><p>The goal is not to predict every move. The goal is to build a repeatable process: read context, define risk, wait for confirmation, accept invalidation, and review honestly.</p></div></article><aside class="space-y-5"><a class="terminal-card card-hover block p-5" href="/about/evidence-policy/"><h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold">Evidence Policy</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">How claims are labeled, checked, and reviewed.</p></a><a class="terminal-card card-hover block p-5" href="/about/risk-policy/"><h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold">Risk Policy</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Why risk is visible across the site.</p></a></aside></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
